## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="b3747-102">発生したとき、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>と<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>イベントのインスタンスを渡す<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>関連イベントのハンドラーにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-102">When they are raised, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> events pass an instance of  <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> to  the handler for the associated event.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="b3747-103"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A>オーディオの新しいレベルの入力時にプロパティを取得、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>または<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>イベントが発生します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-103">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A> property gets the new level of audio input when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType> event is raised.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="b3747-104">`AudioLevel`のプロパティ、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>と<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>クラスは、音声認識エンジンにオーディオの入力の現在のレベルを提供します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-104">The `AudioLevel` property of the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> classes provides the current level of the audio input to the speech recognition engine.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="b3747-105">次の例は、イベント ハンドラーを追加、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-105">The following example adds an event handler to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b3747-106">ハンドラーは、コンソールに新しいオーディオ レベルを出力します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-106">The handler outputs the new audio level to the console.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="b3747-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> は、<xref:System.EventArgs> から派生します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3747-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  

```csharp  

private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  

// Initialize the SpeechRecognitionEngine object.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  

  // Add an event handler for the AudioLevelUpdated event.  
  sre.AudioLevelUpdated += new EventHandler<AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>(sre_AudioLevelUpdated);  

  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  

// Write the audio level to the console when the AudioLevelUpdated event is raised.  
void sre_AudioLevelUpdated(object sender, AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs e)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("The audio level is now: {0}.", e.AudioLevel);  
}  

```
